{"id":892870,"date":[{"year":1992,"month":12,"day":22}],"page":"7","source":"《国际展望》","region":"","masthead":"中外文摘","special_issue":"中外文摘","column":"","genre":"","count":"175","ytitle":"","mtitle":"国际金融发展的10大趋势","ftitle":"","authors":[],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"目前国际金融的发黑可以归纳法以下十大趋势，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(1)金融管制的“宽松化”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(2)金融商品的多样化。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(3)金融机构的多功能化。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(4)金融体系的分散化。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(5)金融市场的国际化。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(6)国际融资的证券化。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(7)金融业务的“时新化”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(8)金融操作的电脑化。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(9)金融格局的多元化。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(10)金融协调的“灵活化”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(摘自《国际展望》)"}]}